*WHY* DOESN'T the American talk shows talk about BTS doing *THIS* .. *INSTEAD OF* the *EXACT SAME BOOOOOOORING QUESTIONS??????*

On American Hustle Life.. I noticed V having a *cast* on his wrist.. how did he *break* it?  And *how* did it *heal* so fast.. that the cast was taken off soon after.. within the two weeks they were staying in L.A?
Would Jimin *EVER* consider doing an "American" version of the Masked Singer?
After their military service.. would *ANY* of them *consider* hosting a *game show???*
Would Jin *EVER* consider acting on American movie screens.. once Covid 19 is over?
Since *their* Idol *Drake* mentioned backstage at an awards show, that he would host BTS when they come to Toronto... would they take his offer seriously???
Does BTS *EVER* respond to YouTube comments *directly*???  And *if* so..  by being themselves or by an alias???
